{"tid":1008734,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"吳卓羲開全國首間figure博物館 展出自己多年收藏珍品 包括價值$13萬1:1 Iron Man","createTime":"2019-02-04T16:41:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-06T08:59:08.000Z","uid":66923,"like":41,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"04ca11bcabb493c06f4a3c72e4b2d61f6107e20c","tid":1008734,"uid":66923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T16:41:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FjwQx8s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFjwQx8s.jpg&h=6323efad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近年好少喺香港電視劇見到吳卓羲，原來佢最近喺北京開咗全國第一間figure博物館。呢個博物館名為《吳卓羲個人雕像模玩博物館》，展出咗佢收藏嘅超级英雄figure，包括Marvel、DC都有。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D3oWtGY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD3oWtGY.jpg&h=b363d5cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之所以會選擇開博物館係因為兩個原因：<br />\n第一，他收藏嘅figure數量實在太多，而每一個figure都要放喺可以完全欣賞到嘅地方，而佢屋企已經放唔落啦！<br />\n第二，吳卓羲屋企養咗幾隻貓，主子好易整爛啲figure。<br />\n而吳卓羲都對figure勁有興趣，想有一個地方俾其他figure狂熱份子交流，所以決定開呢個博物館。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qsaax8U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQsaax8U.jpg&h=a798bde2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個博物館不設門票，展出咗吳卓羲大概三分之一嘅收藏品，另外仲有200幾個figure未運到。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nL9FVnn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnL9FVnn.jpg&h=677887a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oKhkaVJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoKhkaVJ.jpg&h=0f282312&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其中有一個1:1嘅 Iron Man figure，價值成13萬！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hsSsAnu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhsSsAnu.jpg&h=c04820df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/94Djrua.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F94Djrua.jpg&h=4229b9bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然Iron Man仲未運到，但係喺博物館已經有一個1:1嘅蝙蝠俠，全球得10隻，勁珍貴！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6eG1EPh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6eG1EPh.jpg&h=b1a62ea8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tsJvx9i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtsJvx9i.jpg&h=c5285798&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n入面仲有好多figure，每一隻都係吳卓羲親手砌㗎！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ks2DG2L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fks2DG2L.jpg&h=0d75f18f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qPp28HM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqPp28HM.jpg&h=d3ee165c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RjvBtHM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRjvBtHM.jpg&h=ca54d06b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"31c5b7deb1f0f05bc52942224647d3d56ebd62be","tid":1008734,"uid":225734,"like":26,"dislike":4,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T16:46:15.000Z","msg":"唔係咁都要抄古仔嘛? 古仔個倉型好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a20e7110e8f44cd95a49f44cf09e6ca794809420","tid":1008734,"uid":82917,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T16:46:59.000Z","msg":"召喚會員御用衝動撚"},{"pid":"1eaee5caa2a0b435577b057044901aae01998a5b","tid":1008734,"uid":167658,"like":63,"dislike":1,"score":62,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T16:48:18.000Z","msg":"就咁放出黎，一日就俾蝗仔玩爛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a9abf55a2849dfcdb06c12ce0ac6c1c3f29fb90","tid":1008734,"uid":49853,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T16:48:40.000Z","msg":"古天樂：睇完嚇左一跳，然後得啖笑"},{"pid":"46688972b0c6778f9b93cdef3be4dddeeeabe56e","tid":1008734,"uid":3768,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T16:54:46.000Z","msg":"係大陸開過幾日佢d收藏一係爛晒一係俾人偷晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"526a6b9be5ccbad9c6e36e618fe4d9727dba2ae7","tid":1008734,"uid":44044,"like":7,"dis